# Halyvernoxian App Architecture

## App Overview
Halyvernoxian is a couples-focused Flutter application with four main features:
- Love Diary: For tracking relationship milestones and memories
- Perfect Luggage: For trip planning and packing lists
- Cartoon Generator: For AI-generated couple cartoons
- Profile: For user settings and information

## Project Structure
The app follows a clean architecture with these layers:
- Presentation (UI): Screens and widgets
- Domain (Business Logic): Models and business rules
- Data: Local storage with shared_preferences

## Key Requirements
- Use setState for state management (no complex state management libraries)
- Use shared_preferences for data persistence
- Chinese language UI
- Dark theme with deep blue and purple colors
- No external fonts, no assets/images directory
- No account functionality required
- No freezed package or part syntax
- No cached_network_image

## Feature Details
1. Love Diary:
   - Add relationship details (birth dates, gender selection)
   - Track love days counter
   - Milestone reminders (birthdays, anniversaries)
   - Memory timeline

2. Perfect Luggage:
   - Trip planning
   - Packing lists with completion tracking
   - Reminders before trips

3. Cartoon Generator:
   - Text-to-image generation for couple cartoons
   - Must include a boy and girl in cartoon output
   - History of generated images

4. Profile:
   - User information
   - App settings
   - Relationship statistics
